# MMASH Circadian Analysis – Data Flow

Reminder: install a Mermaid preview extension in VS Code to render the diagram below.

```mermaid
graph TD
	%% Focus on data flow steps
	raw["MMASH CSV inputs"] --> extract["Feature extraction (sleep, HRV, activity, questionnaires)"]
	extract --> train["Model train / update (Random Forest)"]
	train --> artifacts["Model + scaler artifacts"]
	artifacts --> predict["CLI prediction run"]
	extract --> predict
	predict --> score["Circadian score + recommendations"]
```
